This topic describes how to use the <%= vars.product_full %> Command Line Interface (<%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> CLI) to view information about the plans available for deploying a <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> cluster.  

1. <%= partial 'login-api' %>

1. Run the following command to view information about the available plans for deploying a cluster:  

    ```
    $ tkgi plans
    ```
    
    The response lists details about the available plans, including plan names and descriptions:  
    ```console
    $ tkgi plans
    
    Name     ID  Description
    default      Default plan for K8s cluster
    ```
